N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4215.17 - Daily reports to commission

State Regulations

Complete and detailed records of each race, containing
each change of readings of the odds and the actual possible payoff on each
horse, shall be filed with the commission at the end of each racing
day. Notes
